description._content: Description: A beauty spot at the Oil-Fields. A fern grotte behind Kalgah, beside a small brook, tributary to the Tembi. Location: Kalgah, Tembi, Persia Description: A fern grotte in the valley behind Kalgah. Location: Kalgah, Persia Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/714 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives.
